text: Magne Kvalvik (born 3 July 1973) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's lightweight double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Porsgrunn
